ManualReject is an ActionForm
    action is ManualReject
    Layout
        header3 of "EnterYourReasonForRejecting<TaskName>"
        visible when (RejectReasonCodeRequired)
            paragraph
                reason code
                reason code.Description
                    no label
                    display as text
        single column
            PrmComment
                no label
                use text area of 10 lines
